text: Erika Vilūnaitė (born 25 December 1980) is a road cyclist from Lithuania. She represented her nation at the 1998 and 2005 UCI Road World Championships. ==References== ==External links== * profile at Procyclingstats.com Category:1980 births Category:Lithuanian female cyclists Category:Living people Category:People from Utena
